  <brief_title>A Study to Evaluate the Efficacy Between Helicobacter Pylori Eradication Therapy and Motilitone in Functional Dyspepsia</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Multicenter, Randomized, Double-blind Comparative Study to Evaluate the Efficacy Between Helicobacter Pylori Eradication Therapy and Motilitone in Functional Dyspepsia</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
