  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a clinical study to evaluate the efficacy between Helicobacter pylori Eradication
      therapy and Motilitone in Functional Dyspepsia
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      This is a multicenter, randomized, double-blind comparative clinical study to evaluate the
      efficacy between Helicobacter pylori Eradication therapy and Motilitone in Functional
      Dyspepsia
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
